Actions.Text: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS
COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO RULES

Title: Increases the tax on deeds in the city of Mount Vernon
Summary: Increases the tax on deeds in the city of Mount Vernon to 1 1/2 percent.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to increasing the tax on deeds in the city of Mount Vernon
